<span class="line"><span>  </span></span>
<span class="line"><span>&#x3C;h5>el表达式和java代码的不同&#x3C;/h5>  </span></span>
<span class="line"><span>&#x3C;h6>用java代码获取值时可能出现null的情况&#x3C;/h6>  </span></span>
