<span class="line"><span>  </span></span>
<span class="line"><span>&#x3C;h4>使用el表达式获取域中引用类型&#x3C;/h4>  </span></span>
<span class="line"><span>&#x3C;h5>域中存储的是对象时&#x3C;/h5>  </span></span>
